SubjectBy-elections (4) - Calgary Heritage - Calgary Midnapore - Markham-Thornhill - Saint-Laurent
PrecisOrder directing that WRITS OF ELECTION do issue in order to fill the vacancies in the House of Commons for the electoral districts of Calgary Heritage - Calgary Midnapore -Markham-Thornhill - Saint-Laurent , with polling to take place on April 3, 2017.
